# Native State effect provider

```scalascript
val first = runState(10) {
  val before = State.get()
  State.modify(x => x + 5)
  State.set(State.get() + 2)
  before * 2
}

val nested = runState(1) {
  State.set(2);
  (runState(100) {
     State.set(101)
     State.get()
   }, State.get())
}

println(first._1)
println(first._2)
println(nested._1)
println(nested._2._1._1)
println(nested._2._1._2)
println(nested._2._2)
```
